author: amaniatis
msg: CAY-916 Ordering is now able to ignore paths which are not fully resolvable. These are sorted just like other NULLs. Initial code contributed by Marcin Skladaniec who is already covered under the ish group CLA lodged with Apache for this work.
Also, another switch allows the user to specify whether nulls are sorted to the top or bottom.
